TITLE: GraphQL Code Generator Configuration
DESCRIPTION: This TypeScript code defines the configuration for GraphQL Code Generator. It specifies the schema location, document patterns, and output locations for generated code. The `preset` option is set to `client` to generate client-side code. It outputs generated code to `./src/graphql/` and the schema to `./schema.graphql`.
SOURCE: https://github.com/dotansimha/graphql-code-generator/blob/master/website/src/pages/docs/guides/vanilla-typescript.mdx#_snippet_1

