TITLE: Configuring Codegen with Default Fetcher (TypeScript)
DESCRIPTION: Sets up the GraphQL Code Generator configuration (`codegen.ts`) to use the global `fetch` function as the data fetcher for generated React Query hooks. It includes the necessary plugins (`typescript`, `typescript-operations`, `typescript-react-query`) and sets the `fetcher` config option to `'fetch'`. Requires GraphQL schema and operation documents.
