TITLE: Configuring GraphQL Code Generator for GraphQL Yoga (TypeScript)
DESCRIPTION: This configuration snippet, for GraphQL Yoga, exports a 'CodegenConfig' object specifying the schema file and generated type output, using the necessary codegen plugins without advanced configuration. Dependencies include the GraphQL Code Generator plugins, a schema file, and proper TypeScript setup.
SOURCE: https://github.com/dotansimha/graphql-code-generator/blob/master/website/src/pages/docs/guides/graphql-server-apollo-yoga.mdx#_snippet_3

LANGUAGE: typescript
CODE:
```
import type { CodegenConfig } from '@graphql-codegen/cli';

