TITLE: Implementing GraphQL union resolver with non-optional __typename in TypeScript
DESCRIPTION: Illustrates improved resolver pattern where each returned object explicitly declares the __typename property corresponding to its GraphQL union member type. This simplifies the __resolveType function by directly returning the __typename, enabling better TypeScript type inference and clearer resolver logic.
