TITLE: Codegen Config with GraphQL Yoga File Upload Support (TypeScript)
DESCRIPTION: This TypeScript config adapts the GraphQL Code Generator server preset to support GraphQL Yoga's file upload feature by overriding the File scalar type and customizing which resolvers are generated for various GraphQL types. The resolvers generation pattern allows granular control over which files are created for queries, mutations, and objects.
