TITLE: Export interfaces for GraphQL schema with interface implementations
DESCRIPTION: This code demonstrates how the code generator creates `ResolversInterfaceTypes` to map GraphQL interfaces to their implementing types, such as `Fighter` and `Wizard`. Using the `RefType` generic, it enables more accurate type inference for interface-conforming objects and their subclasses in resolver definitions, supporting complex schemas with interface relationships.
