TITLE: Shell script to run GraphQL code generation with Yarn
DESCRIPTION: Adds a build step in Gradle to automatically run the GraphQL code generator before compiling the project. Executes 'yarn graphql-codegen' to generate Java classes based on the configuration, ensuring code is up-to-date during each build.
SOURCE: https://github.com/dotansimha/graphql-code-generator/blob/master/website/src/pages/plugins/java/java-apollo-android.mdx#_snippet_1

LANGUAGE: Shell Script
CODE:
```
preBuild.doFirst {
  def proc = "yarn graphql-codegen".execute()
  proc.waitForProcessOutput(System.out, System.err)
}

build.dependsOn preBuild
```

