TITLE: Override All Names with lowerCase Naming Convention
DESCRIPTION: This code snippet shows how to override the default naming convention for all generated names to `lowerCase`.  The `namingConvention` option is set to `'change-case-all#lowerCase'`, which transforms all generated names to lowercase.
SOURCE: https://github.com/dotansimha/graphql-code-generator/blob/master/website/src/pages/plugins/typescript/typescript-apollo-next.mdx#_snippet_8

LANGUAGE: ts
CODE:
```
import type { CodegenConfig } from '@graphql-codegen/cli'

const config: CodegenConfig = {
  // ...
  generates: {
    'path/to/file': {
      // plugins...
      config: {
        namingConvention: 'change-case-all#lowerCase'
      }
    }
  }
}
export default config
```

